LINUX INSTRUCTIONS
------------------

To install `New Hope`, follow these steps:

  1. Install SDL library, if not already installed <http://www.libsdl.org>
  2. Edit config.mk to adapt settings to your system (usually not needed)
  3. Run `make`
  4. Run `make install` with administrator privileges

That's it. Now just type `newhope` to run the game.
